Package com.vk2gpz.autosell.object

Class AutoSellOptions

java.lang.Object
com.vk2gpz.autosell.object.AutoSellOptions
public class AutoSellOptions extends Object
AutoSellOptions class to hold the configuration options for the AutoSell plugin. This class contains various settings that can be configured for the AutoSell plugin. It includes options for enabling/disabling features, setting intervals, and configuring messages.
